products.title: Dapple Solar Cream Roller Blind
products.description: This range of fabrics feature an effective reflective treatment to the reverse of the fabric to reduce heat and glare keeping your room pleasant in the height of summer whilst also being effective for privacy. This cream roller blind is ideal for rooms that get a lot of sun as the solar coating will help to reflect the light away from your furnishings.
